  "2026-05-24T01:36:07.455Z",codex-active-work,"Evidence: implementation extracted src/cli/commands/annotation-command.ts as the shared annotation command core. comments.ts, notes.ts, and learnings.ts now delegate list/add, limit slicing, author resolution, mutateItem append, result rendering, and ownership wrapping through the shared core while preserving comments stdin/file/includeMeta behavior and notes/learnings legacy audit aliases. Focused tests passed: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/comments-command.spec.ts tests/unit/notes-learnings-command.spec.ts tests/integration/help-runtime.spec.ts --reporter=dot => 3 files / 62 tests."
  "2026-05-24T01:39:31.172Z",codex-active-work,"Release-gate fix: full run-gates initially failed release-readiness coverage alignment because new src/cli/commands/annotation-command.ts was not listed in vitest coverage include. Added it to vitest.config.ts; focused readiness rerun will verify before restarting full gate."
  "2026-05-24T01:44:16.420Z",codex-active-work,"Coverage fix evidence: added helper-edge assertions in tests/unit/comments-command.spec.ts and removed an impossible post-mutation fallback branch in annotation-command.ts. Focused verification passed: PM_RUN_TESTS_SKIP_BUILD=1 node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/comments-command.spec.ts tests/unit/notes-learnings-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts --reporter=dot => 3 files / 66 tests; pnpm exec tsc --noEmit -p tsconfig.json passed."
  "2026-05-24T01:58:24.675Z",codex-active-work,"Final verification evidence: node scripts/release/run-gates.mjs --json --telemetry-mode required --max-sentry-critical 10 --max-sentry-high 20 --max-telemetry-error-rate 10 passed. Gate covered build, typecheck, docs-skills, static quality, coverage 105 files / 1583 tests / 100 percent statements branches functions lines, version policy 2026.5.23, secret scan, npx packed-package smoke, package-first dogfood 84 workflows, npm pack dry-run, compatibility check from base 2026.5.18, and required Sentry/telemetry gate with Sentry critical=0 high=2 total=2 and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=2.94, failures_without_error_code_rows=0."
